      "rationale": "Numerical code verification was performed against the Taylor-Green vortex and Poiseuille channel flow benchmarks. Velocity field errors remained below 0.5% at production mesh resolution, confirming code correctness for the laminar-transitional regime encountered in the pump."
    },
