      "rationale": "In-vitro test conditions were fully documented including blood analog fluid properties, inlet flow rates (2–6 L/min), rotational speeds (2000–3500 RPM), temperature (37°C ± 0.5°C), and hematocrit (35% ± 2%). CFD boundary conditions were set to match measured values. Deviations were within measurement uncertainty."
